Nick LaTour https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nick_LaTour 0 Edgar Daniel Nixon, Jr. (August 1, 1928 – February 28, 2011), better known by his stage name Nick LaTour, was an American television, film, and stage actor. LaTour was the son of African American civil rights leader Edgar Nixon. On February 28, 2011, LaTour died of cancer at the age of 82.
